Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[TextData[StyleBox["3. Conjectures/Observation", "Subsection"]], "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.7597310302523627`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"59a6ef82-dd53-4e77-9ce7-\
547402ca0690"],

Cell["\<\
(i) the data looks like the line y = -x
(ii) it does not look as linear when the upper is close to start that is due \
to less iterations of the random function when they are closer.
(iii) In ListLinePlot you can see that as upper is higher it is more likely \
to hit lower\
